Tulsiramji Gaikwad College Of\nEngineering and Technology

I feel ecstatic to introduce you to Department of Master In Computer Application, which is established in year 2008–2009 and foundation of technology. It is AICTE approved full time two years PG course affiliated by RTM Nagpur University. Department of Master in Computer Application strive for increasing the knowledge, enhancing the critical thinking.

Engineering knowledge: Apply the knowledge of mathematics, science, engineering fundamentals, and an engineering specialization to the solution of complex engineering problems.\nProblem analysis: Identify, formulate, review research literature, and analyze complex engineering problems reaching substantiated conclusions using first principles of mathematics, natural sciences, and engineering sciences.

Vision
To be the source of bringing out globally competent pioneering computing professionals, researchers, innovators and thereby succeed and contribute value to the knowledge-based economy and society.
Mission
To enhance the placement ratio of the department.
To get more industry interaction and partnership with skill India mission.

TGPCET MBA has a history of excellence in the field of management education. It was formed with a single minded purpose of transforming the budding managers into successful leaders .The department has a team of experienced faculty members of the MBA. In addition, over 20 highly experienced visiting faculties from industry take up advanced electives and other subjects.

Apply knowledge of management theories and practices to solve business problems.\nFoster Analytical and Critical thinking abilities for data-based decision making.\nAbility to understand, analyze and communicate global, economic, legal, and ethical areas of business.

Vision
To become learning centre for management by producing professionally committed managers who will contribute in positive sense towards society and nation building at large.
Mission
To be an epitome for higher learning by developing effective leaders and entrepreneurs who anticipate, analyze and manage contemporary as well as emerging business and social issues.

Electrical Engineering is the one of core branch of Engineering. The Department is NBA Accredited from session 2023-24. The basic infrastructure like electrical power plays the major role in the developing economy. The knowledge of fundamentals of electrical engineering is essential for almost all streams. The Department Of Electrical Engineering provides in depth education and prepares its students for all the possible future career and developments in technology.

Engineering Graduates will be able to
 Engineering knowledge
Apply the knowledge of mathematics, science, engineering fundamentals, and an engineering specialization to the solution of complex engineering problems.
Problem analysis
Identify, formulate, review research literature, and analyze complex engineering problems reaching substantiated conclusions using first principles of mathematics, natural sciences, and engineering sciences.

Vision
To emerge as a learning hub and centre of excellence in the domain of Electrical Engineering.
Mission
To disseminate knowledge replete with quality education in the field of Electrical Engineering in meticulous and methodical manner.To provide platform to address societal issues as well as challenges faced by industries.

Library is the heart of our Institution.\nLibrary provides facilities like open stack areas, individual study tables, reference books section, Reprography section etc.\nBook-Bank facility is also offered to toppers and needy students.

1.No transaction will be made without the identify card. I-card shall be nontransferable.
2.Four books will be issued to the students at a time for 15 days.
3.Re-issue will be made for another 10 days, subject to availability and demand of particular book.
4.Students entering the library are required to keep their personal belongings in the property counter.
